Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:11.26,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:15.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:22.83,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:27.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:30.92,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:34.47,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.47,0:00:37.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.30,0:00:45.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Tearing through the\Nair with a Rider Plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:52.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great flight that\Nskates over the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:00:57.07,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up tornadoes with a Rider Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.07,0:01:00.91,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:04.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:08.25,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:11.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:15.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.33,0:01:19.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:24.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(367.167,150.389)}Hongo Takeshi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:24.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx120\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,710.389)}Cannot Transform!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The roads are clearer than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We should make it to the gorge\Nbefore nightfall at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.23,0:01:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was going so well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.13,0:02:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, construction this\Ndeep in the mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.23,0:02:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, nothing to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:18.52,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H372799&}Construction\N{\c&H000000&}Use Detour
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.\NThis one's blocked off, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's wrong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little creeped out...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Let's check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:55.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Be honored!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.81,0:03:00.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You're the first to die to Leech Chameleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.78,0:03:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Your blood will be used to\Nrevive Gel Shocker's monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.66,0:03:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey lady, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A t-terrible monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.73,0:03:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It said... G-Gel Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kid Corps, member number 505.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker spotted!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.22,0:04:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The experiment was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We've brought Ganikomoru back to life\Nusing an infusion of fresh human blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ganikomoru... awaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and suck human blood, so that we\Ncan restore more and more monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare for a grand Gel Shocker attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is something I\Nmust deal with first...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I will defeat that perpetual thorn\Nin our side, the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.47,0:04:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no question.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Gel Shocker base.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.46,0:05:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to thank the Rider Kid Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only way up, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,G6, G7. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on our way now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Has something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing to report.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Time for a shift change.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, our target is General Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black wanted to speak with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in the planning room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,General, emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo's motorbike was\Nsighted near the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And the ones who rode it here, Hongo\NTakeshi and Taki Kazuya, are right before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You recognized us, General Black?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to say, but I'm not General Black!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.86,0:06:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ganikomoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:07:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Damned Gel Shocker... they're\Nbringing monsters back to life?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is merely a Gel Shocker frontline base.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo, Taki... it's time for you to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo... you will die at my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.43,0:07:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you tell me about\NGeneral Black's real base!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now try me, Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform into the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I will transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.59,0:08:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.48,0:09:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's something\Nelse I'm worried about...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rider Corps report said that the\NGel Shocker monster called itself Leech Chameleon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was Ganikomoru that met us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And he was easily beaten...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You think it's a trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We should withdraw for now, either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.77,0:10:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This film will reveal to\Nme all your weaknesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Run that part back one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Measure the length of the instant just\Nbefore he transforms into the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Twelve frames of film.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's half a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Half a second, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Doctor Dee of our science division...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In that brief span of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,he is neither Hongo Takeshi,\Nnor the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He is nothing but a powerless puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Research a way to fight him that\Nmakes use of this weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.62,0:11:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. At once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen... have it finished\Nfirst thing in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:21.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's an insurrection!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:23.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The prisoners have initiated a jailbreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:35.09,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.48,0:11:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to survive and find Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think you can escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.07,0:11:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If we die, Kamen Rider will avenge us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So many of our friends died for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we have to keep fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use... they'll trace\Nus by our blood trails!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll distract the pursuers...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.41,0:12:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You... run!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.04,0:12:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I see a blood stain here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.42,0:12:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Just leave me here and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... come and find me, Gel Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let your death be in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:12:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Leeches!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.25,0:13:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Leech Chameleon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to see Hongo Takeshi in your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the Gel Shocker escapee!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Escapee?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You wasted your time. He's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:14:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that Leech Chameleon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.44,0:14:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Leech Chameleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself, Leech Chameleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.19,0:14:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Avenge my comrades...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy Gel Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.85,0:14:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the Gel Shocker escapee?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I am. Please... avenge them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.03,0:15:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Damned Gel Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they're using human blood to bring\Ntheir monsters back from the dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so much calmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.49,0:15:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should rest a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,While I stay here, they could be\Nsacrificing more of my imprisoned comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no time to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll settle things with\NGeneral Black this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.14,0:15:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back with good news, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.03,0:15:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watch us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You think they'll make it\Nsafely to Gel Shocker's base?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You know those two. They'll get it done!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.54,0:16:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Kamen Rider Kid Corps HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.32,0:16:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo? Mr. Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:22.54,Italics,,0,0,0,,Attention, members of the\NKamen Rider Kid Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gel Shocker leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:29.93,Italics,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker is about to mount\Na major attack on Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.93,0:16:33.94,Italics,,0,0,0,,But we intend to slaughter\Nall of our enemies first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.94,0:16:35.53,Italics,,0,0,0,,That includes you, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Try and beat us, if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.98,0:16:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:41.73,Italics,,0,0,0,,If you think I'm lying,\Nlook up at the ceiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Leeches!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, take them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Back me up at the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.66,0:17:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone shows up, I'll stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo. Will you be all right alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.64,0:17:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You... get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.07,0:18:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, spare me! Spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to save you! Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.21,0:18:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.44,0:18:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's taking a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He certainly is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use your blood to\Nrevive another monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.90,0:18:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.81,0:18:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.08,0:18:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.21,0:19:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen to Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the last remaining\Nopposition to Gel Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Leech Chameleon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It took you this long to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Hongo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:20:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This was all a trap to\Nlure you into our base!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Leech Chameleon... What did you do to Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've captured all of your allies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out the other window!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see it, Hongo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Hongo... perhaps I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You got them all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.41,0:20:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Their blood will give new\Nlife to our monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you do it, Leech Chameleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And how do you intend to stop me, Hongo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.74,0:21:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Go ahead and escape, if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.37,0:21:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can hold me behind this wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.45,0:21:29.45,Default Top,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.13,0:21:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Kamen Rider stoppage device\Ndevised by Gel Shocker's science team...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolute zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.37,0:21:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've captured Hongo Takeshi alive at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:21:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Learned your lesson?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.80,0:21:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.35,0:22:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.11,0:22:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.26,0:22:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.10,0:22:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch, Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.40,0:22:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,While you watch, I'll drain\Ntheir blood one at a time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.49,0:22:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and transfer it to my monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.88,0:22:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I'll finish with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.49,0:22:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.62,0:22:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin the countdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.96,0:22:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.48,0:22:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Forty seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.93,0:22:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.24,0:22:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.61,0:22:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.27,0:22:44.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's no use. I can't transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.37,0:22:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.59,0:22:56.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi had fallen into\NGel Shocker's fearsome trap,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.47,0:22:59.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,left unable to transform at a crucial time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:02.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will Taki and the others\Nfall prey to their plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.34,0:23:06.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will Takeshi make it out of this crisis?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.09,0:23:10.68,Cont,,0,70,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:13.22,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(276.175,262.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.88,0:23:13.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At last, the leader shows himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.22,0:23:16.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At last, everything will be revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.46,0:23:20.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is trapped\Nimmobile at absolute zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.66,0:23:24.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Leech Chameleon's fangs draw\Ntowards Yuri's neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.69,0:23:26.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:30.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "Gel Shocker Destroyed!\NThe Leader's End!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.74,0:23:30.99,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx120\fs135\bord0.8\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(467.167,450.389)}Gel Shocker Destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.74,0:23:30.99,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx110\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,720.389)}The Leader's End!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.18,0:23:39.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,The wind gusts across the wasteland
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:42.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider traverses it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:46.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Alone, all alone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.78,0:23:49.99,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Holding back my sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.99,0:23:53.91,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,I fight, I fight alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.91,0:24:00.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Despite my solitude,\NI will do what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.25,0:24:06.42,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,to protect my friends and my home
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.42,0:24:12.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,I am the Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi Cannot Transform!!